{"tid":496624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有個柒頭跌左野","createTime":"2017-12-12T01:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T14:34:09.000Z","uid":54847,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f8cd3d87d2325d57acba8f3a551e60890d7abe","tid":496624,"uid":54847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"我今朝返工喺樂富地鐵站對出嘅地方<br />\n執到個有牌子嘅card holder<br />\n<br />\n葉小姐如果見到呢個post<br />\n快啲去地鐵站攞返<br />\n我交左比地鐵站嘅客務中心<br />\n因為我趕住返工 冇時間拎去差館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n客務中心哥哥話佢地會登記呢啲失物<br />\n喺任何一個地鐵站嘅客務中心都可以查到嘅<br />\n<br />\n唔知葉小姐會唔會見到呢個post<br />\n希望見到啦 唔見左card holder都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次唔好咁唔小心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702e1ebd9e1531bb013fed879a3a4f62d6a778f2","tid":496624,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:14:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07de8c3fe14c3f23c443ccae703a4791a912ba45","tid":496624,"uid":22231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇跌右嘢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8021fd99b828d9c02044dd2f46429b90d8cf7694","tid":496624,"uid":54847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"輕輕幫你一推"},{"pid":"bc6d5abd1904a3ae863f2dd56c35d8a22474806b","tid":496624,"uid":54847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"推啊"}]}